<p>3<br/>they will be comfortable in it.<br/>Glad to hear Caleb is behaving himself. I wouldn't mind him chained outside my tent to keep away the native tradesmen, making call at all hours of the day and night with something to sell which as a rule is trumpery.<br/>Please excuse pencil. Ink is a scarcity here.<br/>Have a heavy day tomorrow so will turn in with love from<br/>Your affectate Son<br/>Terence</p>
